    "description": [
      "Soft murmurs from elven voices drift from the open windows of low, screened-in villas lining the street.  The aspens lend privacy to their front gardens, coming together to form a circular court at the walkway's end.  At the apex of the court, a two-story modwir building with several wide windows welcomes patrons.  Birds twitter from the branches of the ancient yew tree standing in the center of the marae, yet not a single stain mars the benches beneath its outer branches."
